                                        you say?</b><br />
                                    Since the lender is authorized to use the Automated Clearing House System, they
                                    must adhere to NACHA rules and regulations. The amount to be withdrawn from your
                                    account will be the amount that you authorized.
                                    <br />
                                    <br />
                                    <b>FAQ: If sufficient funds will not be available on the loan due date, what should
